  year        = {2026},
  note        = {We study side effect prediction for robotic manipulation, aiming to anticipate unintended changes before they occur, so the robot can stop, resample, or defer to a human. We train a side effect critic, initialized from a pre-trained vision-language action (VLA) model, that predicts whether given action chunks will cause a side effect before the actions are executed.},
